title: 207 - R.I.P. Stephen E. Wilhite AKA Dr. Gif
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off as the boys wish Zito and Brucy flap jacks their best as they are in transit to Dallas Texas for Wreslemania!!! The boys all catch up on their latest show and movie recommendations and then jump right into the Pod FOD. The Pod FOD which is a folder compiled of all things from the internet. Todays FOD includes the reactions to the official top gun trailer, a rise in average life expectancy, the news of no National Treasure 3, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
